T*
() Tj
T*
(This document defines active monetary policy and fee routing under current consensus constants.) Tj
T*
(- Accounting Units) Tj
T*
(- All consensus accounting is integer-atom based.) Tj
T*
(- 1 ATHO = 1,000,000,000 atoms.) Tj
T*
(- Reward Schedule \(Current\)) Tj
T*
(- Block time target: 120 seconds.) Tj
T*
(- Blocks/year: 262,800.) Tj
T*
