T*
(- Era 8: 0.78125 ATHO/block) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Bootstrap and pre-tail totals:) Tj
T*
(- One-time bootstrap allocation: 781,250 ATHO at block 1.) Tj
T*
(- Pre-tail subsidy target: 399,218,750 ATHO.) Tj
T*
(- Total pre-tail base target = 399,218,750 + 781,250 = 400,000,000 ATHO.) Tj
T*
(- Hard max supply cap = 500,000,000 ATHO.) Tj
T*
(- Supply-closure check: 399,218,750 + 781,250 + 100,000,000 = 500,000,000.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Tail:) Tj
T*
(- Tail reward 0.1953125 ATHO/block from height 17,000,000 onward.) Tj
T*
(- Tail activation occurs at ~64.69 years from genesis.) Tj
T*
(- Tail annual issuance: 51,328.125 ATHO/year.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Hard-cap clipping rule:) Tj
T*
(- Subsidy is clipped at coinbase path by remaining cap headroom.) Tj
T*
(- Once total_emitted_atoms reaches 500,000,000 ATHO, subsidy is 0 for all later heights.) Tj
T*
(- Fee routing/burn/pool accounting remains unchanged \(fees do not mint new supply\).) Tj
T*
(- Monetary Anchors) Tj
T*
(Atho uses three monetary anchors:) Tj
T*
(- 400,000,000 ATHO base issuance path.) Tj
T*
(- 500,000,000 ATHO hard max supply cap.) Tj
T*
(- 21,000,000 ATHO protected supply floor.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Design intent:) Tj
T*
(- Base path controls deterministic launch distribution.) Tj
T*
(- Max cap bounds long-run mint expansion.) Tj
T*
(- Floor bounds long-run burn pressure.) Tj
T*
(- Active Fee Policy) Tj
T*
(Current constants:) Tj
T*
(- FEE_PER_BYTE_ATOMS = 500 \(policy unit is vsize\)) Tj
T*
