(- MIN_TRANSACTION_FEE_ATOMS = 200,000) Tj
T*
(- DUST_LIMIT_ATOMS = 20,000 \(1/10 of MIN_TRANSACTION_FEE_ATOMS\)) Tj
T*
(- Max block base cap: 3,500,000 bytes) Tj
T*
(- Max block weight: 14,000,000) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Fee routing:) Tj
T*
(- Pre-tail: 40% of total fees route to consensus pool \(20% miner bucket, 20% stake bucket\).) Tj
T*
(- Post-tail: 55% of total fees route to consensus pool \(25% miner bucket, 30% stake bucket\).) Tj
T*
(- At tail, routed non-pool fees \(45%\) are burn-targeted \(100% burn policy\), clipped by) Tj
T*
(supply-floor headroom.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Supply floor:) Tj
T*
(- Effective circulating supply is clipped to never go below 21,000,000 ATHO.) Tj
T*
(- Throughput Formulas) Tj
T*
(Let:) Tj
T*
(- Bv = 3,500,000 effective vbytes per block cap) Tj
T*
(- T = 120 seconds) Tj
T*
(- Savg = average non-coinbase tx vsize) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Then:) Tj
T*
(- tx_per_block = Bv / Savg) Tj
T*
(- TPS = tx_per_block / T) Tj
T*
(- Post-Tail Net Supply Math) Tj
T*
(At full block utilization by vbytes:) Tj
T*
(- Total fee floor capacity per block = 3,500,000 * 500 = 1,750,000,000 atoms = 1.75 ATHO) Tj
T*
(- Annual total fees at full utilization = 459,900 ATHO/year) Tj
T*
(- Burnable routed share \(45%\) at full utilization = 206,955 ATHO/year) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Post-tail net annual change:) Tj
T*
(- Delta_supply = 51,328.125 - \(206,955 * utilization\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Deflation threshold:) Tj
T*
(- utilization ~= 51,328.125 / 206,955 ~= 0.24802 \(24.802%\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Interpretation:) Tj
T*
(- <24.802% utilization: inflationary net.) Tj
T*
(- =24.802%: neutral net.) Tj
T*
(- >24.802%: deflationary net \(subject to floor clipping\).) Tj
T*
(- Milestones) Tj
T*
(- Pre-tail complete at height 16,999,999: 400,000,000 ATHO emitted total.) Tj
T*
(- Tail starts at height 17,000,000.) Tj
T*
(- Tail subsidy headroom to hard cap: 100,000,000 ATHO.) Tj
T*
(- Tail blocks required to exhaust hard-cap headroom: 512,000,000 blocks.) Tj
T*
(- Last positive-subsidy height: 528,999,999 \(~2012.94 years from genesis\).) Tj
T*
(- First zero-subsidy height after cap clip: 529,000,000 \(~2012.94 years from genesis\).) Tj
T*
(- Time from tail start to subsidy shutdown: ~1,948.25 years.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
